Frontend development ke liye Firebase ka istemal karne ke liye kuch mukhya topics hain jo aapko cover karna chahiye:

Firebase Setup:

Firebase project create karna aur Firebase SDK ko apne project mein integrate karna.
Authentication:

User authentication implement karna Firebase Authentication service ka istemal karke.
Firestore Database:

Real-time database interactions ke liye Firestore database setup karna aur data ko store aur retrieve karna.
Storage:

Files, images, aur other assets ko store karne ke liye Firebase Storage ka istemal karna.
Hosting:

Frontend web application ko Firebase Hosting par deploy karna.
Analytics:

User behavior aur app performance ka track rakhne ke liye Firebase Analytics ka istemal karna.
Cloud Functions:

Serverless backend logic run karne ke liye Firebase Cloud Functions ka istemal karna.
Authentication Providers:

Different authentication providers (Google, Facebook, Email/Password) ka setup karke users ko multiple login options provide karna.
Security Rules:

Firebase Security Rules ka istemal karke data access aur security ko configure karna.
Yeh topics aapko Fire